WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:15.000
Storylines, Level 1

00:15.000 --> 00:22.000
The Locks Rule, by Peter

00:22.000 --> 00:29.000
Where am I?

00:29.000 --> 00:33.000
Where am I?

00:33.000 --> 00:35.000
I don't know.

00:35.000 --> 00:39.000
I'm in a beautiful room in an old house.

00:39.000 --> 00:45.000
There's a bed, an expensive chair, and a beautiful table.

00:45.000 --> 00:50.000
I can't see anything from the window, only a green field.

00:50.000 --> 00:53.000
The sun is shining on the field.

00:53.000 --> 00:57.000
I can hear music, quiet music.

00:57.000 --> 00:59.000
It's Mozart.

00:59.000 --> 01:02.000
Why am I here?

01:02.000 --> 01:04.000
I don't know.

01:04.000 --> 01:07.000
Oh, my head is hurting.

01:07.000 --> 01:12.000
I can't open the door, and I can't open the window.

01:12.000 --> 01:17.000
I'm wearing grey trousers and a grey shirt.

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
I'm not wearing any shoes.

01:20.000 --> 01:23.000
I'm hungry and I'm thirsty.

01:23.000 --> 01:26.000
There isn't any food in the room.

01:26.000 --> 01:28.000
There isn't a drink either.

01:28.000 --> 01:32.000
There's a pen and some paper on the table.

01:32.000 --> 01:35.000
There isn't anything on the paper.

01:35.000 --> 01:37.000
Who am I?

01:37.000 --> 01:40.000
I can't remember.

01:40.000 --> 01:42.000
I can't remember my name.

01:42.000 --> 01:45.000
I can't remember anything.

01:45.000 --> 01:48.000
Oh, my head hurts a lot.

01:48.000 --> 01:51.000
I'm very tired.

01:51.000 --> 01:54.000
I'm going to sleep.

01:59.000 --> 02:01.000
It's morning.

02:01.000 --> 02:03.000
I'm on the bed.

02:03.000 --> 02:05.000
I'm wearing the grey clothes.

02:05.000 --> 02:08.000
I'm very hungry and very thirsty.

02:08.000 --> 02:09.000
I can hear music again.

02:09.000 --> 02:11.000
It's the Mozart again.

02:11.000 --> 02:14.000
My head doesn't hurt now.

02:14.000 --> 02:17.000
I can't remember my name.

02:17.000 --> 02:20.000
I can't remember anything.

02:20.000 --> 02:22.000
I can hear someone.

02:22.000 --> 02:25.000
There's someone outside the room.

02:25.000 --> 02:28.000
The door is opening.

02:28.000 --> 02:31.000
He's in the room.

02:31.000 --> 02:35.000
He's wearing black trousers and a black shirt.

02:35.000 --> 02:38.000
I don't know him.

02:38.000 --> 02:40.000
Hello. How's your head?

02:40.000 --> 02:42.000
My head.

02:42.000 --> 02:44.000
It doesn't hurt now.

02:44.000 --> 02:46.000
Good. Where am I?

02:46.000 --> 02:48.000
You don't know? No.

02:48.000 --> 02:50.000
Are you thirsty?

02:50.000 --> 02:52.000
Yes. I'm hungry and thirsty.

02:52.000 --> 02:55.000
Drink this.

02:55.000 --> 02:57.000
He's got a glass in his hand.

02:57.000 --> 03:00.000
I drink from the glass.

03:04.000 --> 03:07.000
I'm very tired again.

03:07.000 --> 03:10.000
I'm going to sleep.

03:13.000 --> 03:15.000
What time is it?

03:15.000 --> 03:18.000
My head's hurting again.

03:18.000 --> 03:22.000
I'm on the bed and the room is dark.

03:22.000 --> 03:24.000
I can't hear music now.

03:24.000 --> 03:27.000
I'm going to turn on the light.

03:27.000 --> 03:29.000
Now I can see.

03:29.000 --> 03:32.000
There's a glass on the table.

03:32.000 --> 03:34.000
I'm thirsty again.

03:34.000 --> 03:37.000
I'm going to drink from the glass.

03:42.000 --> 03:45.000
Sleep.

03:45.000 --> 03:48.000
I'm going to sleep.

03:48.000 --> 03:49.000
Wake up.

03:49.000 --> 03:50.000
What?

03:50.000 --> 03:52.000
Oh, my head.

03:52.000 --> 03:54.000
I'm going to ask you some questions.

03:54.000 --> 03:55.000
Who are you?

03:55.000 --> 03:56.000
I don't know.

03:56.000 --> 03:57.000
What's your name?

03:57.000 --> 03:58.000
I don't know.

03:58.000 --> 03:59.000
I'm going to ask you again.

03:59.000 --> 04:00.000
What's your name?

04:00.000 --> 04:01.000
I can't tell you.

04:01.000 --> 04:02.000
I don't know.

04:02.000 --> 04:03.000
Where are you from?

04:03.000 --> 04:04.000
I don't know.

04:04.000 --> 04:05.000
Drink this.

04:05.000 --> 04:06.000
No. I can't.

04:06.000 --> 04:08.000
You're going to drink it.

04:08.000 --> 04:10.000
Do you understand?

04:10.000 --> 04:12.000
There's a gun in his head.

04:12.000 --> 04:14.000
I drink from the glass.

04:14.000 --> 04:18.000
The room is dark.

04:18.000 --> 04:26.000
Two.

04:26.000 --> 04:28.000
Questions?

04:28.000 --> 04:32.000
I'm awake again.

04:32.000 --> 04:34.000
It's quiet outside.

04:34.000 --> 04:37.000
The sun is shining outside the window.

04:37.000 --> 04:39.000
There's food and water on the table.

04:39.000 --> 04:41.000
I'm not tired now.

04:41.000 --> 04:43.000
My head's okay.

04:43.000 --> 04:45.000
Someone's coming.

04:45.000 --> 04:47.000
The door opens.

04:47.000 --> 04:52.000
It's the man in black clothes.

04:52.000 --> 04:54.000
Do you want to talk now?

04:54.000 --> 04:55.000
What about?

04:55.000 --> 04:56.000
Okay.

04:56.000 --> 04:57.000
Who are you?

04:57.000 --> 04:58.000
Who are you?

04:58.000 --> 04:59.000
I'm asking the questions.

04:59.000 --> 05:00.000
Why are you here?

05:00.000 --> 05:02.000
You tell me.

05:02.000 --> 05:06.000
Then he hits me.

05:06.000 --> 05:08.000
He hits me across the face.

05:08.000 --> 05:10.000
We're going to start again.

05:10.000 --> 05:11.000
Who are you?

05:11.000 --> 05:12.000
I can't remember.

05:12.000 --> 05:14.000
Don't hit me.

05:14.000 --> 05:18.000
But he does.

05:18.000 --> 05:21.000
Then he opens the door and he goes.

05:21.000 --> 05:25.000
There's a bump on the back of my head.

05:25.000 --> 05:27.000
It doesn't hurt now,

05:27.000 --> 05:29.000
but my face hurts.

05:29.000 --> 05:31.000
A bump.

05:31.000 --> 05:34.000
I can remember something.

05:34.000 --> 05:37.000
I can remember.

05:37.000 --> 05:39.000
I'm in a field.

05:39.000 --> 05:42.000
I'm lying under a tree.

05:42.000 --> 05:46.000
I've got some binoculars in my hand.

05:46.000 --> 05:48.000
I'm watching a house.

05:48.000 --> 05:52.000
It's a beautiful old house.

05:52.000 --> 05:56.000
Then there's a noise behind me.

05:56.000 --> 05:58.000
It's a man with a dog.

05:58.000 --> 06:00.000
A big dog.

06:00.000 --> 06:03.000
The man's holding a gun.

06:03.000 --> 06:05.000
Then the man's hitting me.

06:05.000 --> 06:09.000
He's hitting me on the head with the gun.

06:09.000 --> 06:12.000
Then everything's going dark.

06:12.000 --> 06:16.000
I've got a bump on my head now.

06:16.000 --> 06:17.000
Why?

06:17.000 --> 06:19.000
Why am I in that field?

06:19.000 --> 06:21.000
Who am I?

06:21.000 --> 06:23.000
Am I a policeman?

06:23.000 --> 06:25.000
Am I a spy?

06:25.000 --> 06:26.000
And who is the man?

06:26.000 --> 06:27.000
Is he a policeman?

06:27.000 --> 06:29.000
Is he a spy?

06:29.000 --> 06:31.000
Or is he a criminal?

06:31.000 --> 06:34.000
I don't know.

06:34.000 --> 06:37.000
But now I can remember something.

06:37.000 --> 06:38.000
Tomorrow.

06:38.000 --> 06:42.000
Tomorrow, I'm going to remember some more.

06:59.000 --> 07:00.000
Three.

07:00.000 --> 07:02.000
No more time.

07:04.000 --> 07:06.000
The next day.

07:06.000 --> 07:10.000
The man with black clothes is in the room again.

07:10.000 --> 07:12.000
Well, how are you today?

07:12.000 --> 07:13.000
I'm okay.

07:13.000 --> 07:14.000
Can you remember anything?

07:14.000 --> 07:15.000
Yes.

07:15.000 --> 07:16.000
A little.

07:16.000 --> 07:17.000
Who are you working for?

07:17.000 --> 07:18.000
I don't know.

07:18.000 --> 07:19.000
Why are you watching us?

07:19.000 --> 07:21.000
I don't know.

07:21.000 --> 07:22.000
Who are you?

07:22.000 --> 07:23.000
Tell me.

07:23.000 --> 07:24.000
Then.

07:24.000 --> 07:25.000
Maybe I can remember.

07:25.000 --> 07:26.000
Very clever.

07:26.000 --> 07:28.000
I can't tell you anything.

07:28.000 --> 07:30.000
He goes out.

07:31.000 --> 07:33.000
I remember again.

07:33.000 --> 07:35.000
I'm watching the house.

07:35.000 --> 07:36.000
It's evening.

07:36.000 --> 07:39.000
I'm wearing a blue coat.

07:39.000 --> 07:42.000
There are lights in the house.

07:42.000 --> 07:44.000
A car's going to the house.

07:44.000 --> 07:46.000
It's a white jaguar.

07:46.000 --> 07:48.000
I'm watching carefully.

07:48.000 --> 07:51.000
I can see two people.

07:51.000 --> 07:53.000
They've got a box.

07:53.000 --> 07:55.000
Then.

07:55.000 --> 07:58.000
Then there's the noise behind me.

07:59.000 --> 08:01.000
And the bump on the head.

08:03.000 --> 08:04.000
It's dark.

08:04.000 --> 08:06.000
I can hear voices outside the room.

08:06.000 --> 08:08.000
Well, he's going to talk.

08:08.000 --> 08:09.000
Maybe.

08:09.000 --> 08:11.000
You can't remember anything because of the bump on his head.

08:11.000 --> 08:12.000
What about the drinks?

08:12.000 --> 08:14.000
No, the drinks aren't helping us.

08:14.000 --> 08:15.000
Okay.

08:15.000 --> 08:16.000
Two days more.

08:16.000 --> 08:18.000
Then that's it.

08:18.000 --> 08:20.000
We haven't got any more time.

08:20.000 --> 08:21.000
How much does he know?

08:21.000 --> 08:23.000
That's the important thing.

08:29.000 --> 08:31.000
Four.

08:31.000 --> 08:33.000
Out of the locked room.

08:37.000 --> 08:38.000
I hear a key.

08:38.000 --> 08:41.000
They're putting a key into the lock.

08:41.000 --> 08:43.000
They're turning the key.

08:43.000 --> 08:46.000
They're locking the door.

08:46.000 --> 08:48.000
They're walking away.

08:48.000 --> 08:51.000
But the key is in the lock.

08:51.000 --> 08:53.000
Two days more.

08:53.000 --> 08:54.000
And that's it.

08:54.000 --> 08:56.000
What are they going to do?

08:57.000 --> 08:59.000
I can't stay here.

08:59.000 --> 09:01.000
The keys in the lock.

09:03.000 --> 09:06.000
I've got some paper from the table.

09:06.000 --> 09:07.000
Now.

09:07.000 --> 09:09.000
Put the paper on.

09:09.000 --> 09:12.000
Push the paper under the.

09:12.000 --> 09:14.000
The papers.

09:14.000 --> 09:16.000
Under the door.

09:16.000 --> 09:17.000
Now.

09:17.000 --> 09:19.000
Take the pen.

09:19.000 --> 09:21.000
Push the pen.

09:21.000 --> 09:23.000
Into the lock.

09:23.000 --> 09:25.000
Yes, there's the key.

09:25.000 --> 09:27.000
It's in the lock.

09:27.000 --> 09:29.000
Push the key with the pen.

09:29.000 --> 09:31.000
Yes.

09:31.000 --> 09:33.000
The key is falling from the lock.

09:33.000 --> 09:35.000
Is it on the paper?

09:35.000 --> 09:38.000
Oh, I don't know.

09:38.000 --> 09:40.000
Pull the paper under the door.

09:40.000 --> 09:44.000
Pull it slowly and carefully.

09:44.000 --> 09:49.000
Very slowly and very carefully.

09:49.000 --> 09:52.000
It's coming under the door.

09:52.000 --> 09:54.000
And there's the key.

09:54.000 --> 09:55.000
It's on the paper.

09:55.000 --> 09:57.000
I've got the key.

09:57.000 --> 10:00.000
I can open the door.

10:00.000 --> 10:02.000
It's quiet outside.

10:02.000 --> 10:08.000
I'm opening the door very quietly and carefully.

10:08.000 --> 10:10.000
There's a corridor.

10:10.000 --> 10:12.000
It's empty.

10:12.000 --> 10:14.000
I'm going out.

10:14.000 --> 10:15.000
Now.

10:15.000 --> 10:21.000
I'm going to take the key.

10:21.000 --> 10:23.000
I'm walking along the corridor.

10:23.000 --> 10:25.000
It's a beautiful house.

10:25.000 --> 10:29.000
I can hear the music again, the Mozart.

10:29.000 --> 10:31.000
There are a lot of doors.

10:31.000 --> 10:35.000
At the end, I can see stairs.

10:35.000 --> 10:37.000
I can hear people downstairs.

10:37.000 --> 10:40.000
I can't go down.

10:40.000 --> 10:43.000
I open some doors.

10:43.000 --> 10:45.000
There are bedrooms.

10:45.000 --> 10:47.000
I open four or five doors.

10:47.000 --> 10:50.000
Then I open another door.

10:50.000 --> 10:53.000
The room is full of paintings.

10:53.000 --> 10:54.000
Things.

10:54.000 --> 10:57.000
Picasos, Rembrandts, Van Gogh.

10:57.000 --> 10:59.000
Oh, they're beautiful.

10:59.000 --> 11:01.000
They're on the floor.

11:01.000 --> 11:03.000
Millions of pounds in this room.

11:03.000 --> 11:05.000
Millions.

11:05.000 --> 11:07.000
I look at a Picasso.

11:07.000 --> 11:11.000
It's the famous stolen Picasso from the London Art Gallery.

11:11.000 --> 11:13.000
Who are they?

11:13.000 --> 11:16.000
There are thieves.

11:16.000 --> 11:19.000
But who am I?

11:19.000 --> 11:24.000
I closed the door.

11:24.000 --> 11:26.000
How can I get out of this house?

11:26.000 --> 11:29.000
They have got guns.

11:29.000 --> 11:31.000
I remember.

11:31.000 --> 11:33.000
One of the bedrooms.

11:33.000 --> 11:35.000
There's a telephone.

11:35.000 --> 11:38.000
I can telephone the police.

11:38.000 --> 11:43.000
I walk quickly along the corridor and open the door.

11:43.000 --> 11:46.000
The telephone is next to the bed.

11:46.000 --> 11:48.000
The number is on the telephone.

11:48.000 --> 11:52.000
Bradstreet, three, five, not seven, two.

11:52.000 --> 11:55.000
I take the telephone carefully.

11:55.000 --> 12:00.000
Nine, nine, nine.

12:00.000 --> 12:03.000
I'm waiting.

12:03.000 --> 12:05.000
Police fire or ambulance?

12:05.000 --> 12:08.000
Police, quickly.

12:08.000 --> 12:11.000
Police, what's your number?

12:11.000 --> 12:14.000
Bradstreet, three, five, nine, seven, two.

12:14.000 --> 12:15.000
Quickly.

12:15.000 --> 12:16.000
I'm a prisoner here.

12:16.000 --> 12:17.000
I can't get out.

12:17.000 --> 12:20.000
The house is full of stolen paintings.

12:20.000 --> 12:21.000
Come quickly.

12:21.000 --> 12:22.000
What's your name?

12:22.000 --> 12:24.000
Come quickly.

12:24.000 --> 12:27.000
This is Bradstreet, three, five, nine, seven, two.

12:27.000 --> 12:29.000
I can't...

12:29.000 --> 12:32.000
Then I hear people in the corridor.

12:32.000 --> 12:34.000
I put down the phone.

12:34.000 --> 12:36.000
I can hear them outside the locked room.

12:36.000 --> 12:38.000
We'll open the door then.

12:38.000 --> 12:39.000
I can't find the key.

12:39.000 --> 12:40.000
Come on.

12:40.000 --> 12:41.000
I can't find it.

12:41.000 --> 12:43.000
There's another key in the kitchen. Get it.

12:43.000 --> 12:44.000
Right.

12:51.000 --> 12:52.000
Five.

12:52.000 --> 12:54.000
Who am I?

12:59.000 --> 13:00.000
Five minutes.

13:00.000 --> 13:02.000
I can hear him again.

13:02.000 --> 13:04.000
He's coming with the key.

13:04.000 --> 13:06.000
He's out in the door.

13:08.000 --> 13:09.000
What?

13:09.000 --> 13:10.000
He isn't here.

13:10.000 --> 13:11.000
What?

13:11.000 --> 13:12.000
But the door's locked.

13:12.000 --> 13:15.000
Find him and take your gun.

13:15.000 --> 13:17.000
And this time, finish him.

13:17.000 --> 13:18.000
You understand?

13:18.000 --> 13:19.000
Okay, I'm going.

13:21.000 --> 13:22.000
I can hear him.

13:22.000 --> 13:24.000
He's opening doors.

13:24.000 --> 13:27.000
Are the police going to come or not?

13:27.000 --> 13:29.000
He's in the next room.

13:31.000 --> 13:32.000
Then I hear them.

13:32.000 --> 13:33.000
Police cars.

13:33.000 --> 13:34.000
A lot of police cars.

13:34.000 --> 13:36.000
They're outside the house.

13:36.000 --> 13:38.000
It's the police.

13:38.000 --> 13:40.000
What do they want?

13:40.000 --> 13:42.000
Don't take the gun with you.

13:42.000 --> 13:44.000
They're going downstairs.

13:44.000 --> 13:46.000
I can hear voices.

13:48.000 --> 13:50.000
Good evening, Inspector.

13:50.000 --> 13:52.000
What can I do for you?

13:52.000 --> 13:54.000
We want to look around the house.

13:54.000 --> 13:56.000
We're looking for some paintings.

13:56.000 --> 13:58.000
But there's nothing here.

13:58.000 --> 13:59.000
Nothing.

13:59.000 --> 14:01.000
We can look then.

14:01.000 --> 14:02.000
But why?

14:02.000 --> 14:04.000
A telephone call.

14:04.000 --> 14:06.000
A telephone call about some paintings.

14:06.000 --> 14:07.000
From?

14:07.000 --> 14:08.000
We don't know.

14:08.000 --> 14:09.000
You don't know?

14:09.000 --> 14:10.000
Well...

14:10.000 --> 14:11.000
The main inspector.

14:11.000 --> 14:13.000
The paintings are up here.

14:13.000 --> 14:14.000
I can show you.

14:14.000 --> 14:15.000
Follow me.

14:16.000 --> 14:18.000
It's ten minutes later.

14:18.000 --> 14:21.000
The man and the woman are in the police cars.

14:21.000 --> 14:23.000
Well, Eddie.

14:23.000 --> 14:24.000
This is a surprise.

14:24.000 --> 14:25.000
Eddie.

14:25.000 --> 14:27.000
Is that my name?

14:27.000 --> 14:28.000
Eddie.

14:28.000 --> 14:29.000
Come on.

14:29.000 --> 14:31.000
No, I can't remember.

14:31.000 --> 14:33.000
You can't remember me.

14:33.000 --> 14:35.000
I can't remember my name.

14:35.000 --> 14:36.000
Eddie.

14:36.000 --> 14:37.000
Eddie, what?

14:37.000 --> 14:39.000
Eddie Hampton.

14:39.000 --> 14:42.000
What are you doing here, Eddie?

14:42.000 --> 14:43.000
I tell him.

14:43.000 --> 14:46.000
I tell him about the field and the binoculars.

14:46.000 --> 14:49.000
I tell him about the bump on my head and the room.

14:49.000 --> 14:52.000
I tell him about the paper and the key.

14:52.000 --> 14:55.000
He's laughing at me.

14:55.000 --> 14:57.000
Okay.

14:57.000 --> 15:00.000
I'm Eddie Hampton, but who's Eddie Hampton?

15:00.000 --> 15:03.000
He's laughing again.

15:04.000 --> 15:05.000
You know me.

15:05.000 --> 15:07.000
Am I a policeman?

15:07.000 --> 15:08.000
No, Eddie.

15:08.000 --> 15:10.000
You aren't a policeman.

15:10.000 --> 15:11.000
Then who am I?

15:11.000 --> 15:13.000
And what am I doing here?

15:13.000 --> 15:15.000
I don't know.

15:15.000 --> 15:17.000
But I can't tell you something.

15:17.000 --> 15:18.000
What?

15:18.000 --> 15:20.000
Eddie Hampton's a criminal.

15:20.000 --> 15:22.000
A thief.

15:22.000 --> 15:24.000
Not a big thief.

15:24.000 --> 15:28.000
Those two people are big thieves with their famous paintings.

15:28.000 --> 15:29.000
No.

15:29.000 --> 15:31.000
You're a small thief, Eddie.

15:31.000 --> 15:39.000
You steal from houses, televisions, radios, videos, high-fives, a little money sometimes.

15:39.000 --> 15:43.000
You're a small, but thank you for your help.

